# Glob patterns (relative to NOTES_ROOT) excluded from indexing.
# By default the whole vault is indexed; you can either exclude sensitive
# folders here (removed from the index entirely) or leave them indexed and
# filter at QUERY time with `search --exclude '<glob>'`.

.obsidian/*
.trash/*
templates/*

# Example: exclude sensitive or noisy areas from the index entirely.
# private/*
# **/secrets/*
